knowledgeGraph.title: Intermountain Health Primary Children's Hospital
knowledgeGraph.type: Hospital in Salt Lake City, Utah
knowledgeGraph.description: Intermountain Primary Children's Hospital is a nationally ranked pediatric acute care children's teaching hospital located in Salt Lake City, Utah. The hospital has 289 pediatric beds and is affiliated with the University of Utah School of Medicine.
